rating_comment: Very calm and homely place that's slightly off the main road. Pretty nice restaurants near by to walk by. Would love to stay there again.

Wonderful clean room with everything I needed. The WiFi worked well, the kitchen had all the necessities, hot water for bathing and a nice quiet location. They were even kind enough to give me a ride to the airport when my taxi didn't show up! Thank you Newa House for the pleasant stay.

Very tidy and lovely home equipped with everything you need. Was there for a night but wud love to visit again and again. Fantastic and cleanliest aura, well mannered staff, lovely vibrance, beautiful ambience, yummy food and well the Best Hosts.

They responded quickly when I needed emergency booking due to canceled flight. Wonderful hosts and the listing was comfortable and exactly as described! Would recommend to anyone needing a stay near the airport.
Very kind and cooperative host. They took care of our basic needs and made sure we felt comfortable during the stay
Nice place to stay. Friendly host.
Everything was perfect. If you are in Siliguri, this is the place you want to stay at, you won't regret.
